  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Hardhat has a `sources` configuration attribute, with the default value `./contracts`. However, any contracts within `./contracts` is compiled both for running tests, but also for operations like `npx hardhat flatten`.\r\n\r\nThere needs to be a separate `./test-contracts` or `./test/contracts` or `./contracts/test` directory into which contracts can be placed to be compiled for use by unit tests, but that are not included in `npx hardhat flatten` or similar operations.",
